Carolyn GILLIAM, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
ATRIUM AT PRINCETON, LLC, t/a Atrium Health, Defendant-Respondent. C-399 September Term 2017
079970 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 8, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002514-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
